574
00:35:06,280 --> 00:35:06,880
Wei,

575
00:35:07,590 --> 00:35:08,280
please go back.

576
00:35:08,920 --> 00:35:10,510
We can protect ourselves.

577
00:35:11,510 --> 00:35:12,440
I told you.

578
00:35:12,590 --> 00:35:13,480
Since you saved my life,

579
00:35:14,000 --> 00:35:14,920
