611
00:37:26,480 --> 00:37:26,960
I won't make a bet with you.

612
00:37:28,110 --> 00:37:29,000
I won't be married off.

613
00:37:29,190 --> 00:37:30,030
I'll just take a live-in husband.

614
00:37:33,230 --> 00:37:34,670
