Empress Dejia,

633
00:38:33,880 --> 00:38:35,030
I am indebted to you.

634
00:38:36,510 --> 00:38:37,190
As a father,

635
00:38:37,550 --> 00:38:39,510
I believed I never owed Jinghe anything,

636
